OL,3,CYoung burglars caught after going for
OL,4,Cbreakfast in stolen car
OL,6,FTwo young burglars who stole a luxury
OL,7,Fcar in Nottinghamshire have been
OL,8,Fsentenced after they were caught on
OL,9,FCCTV going for breakfast in the stolen
OL,10,Fvehicle.
OL,12,FRhys Abbott, 20, and Roman Stevenson,
OL,13,F19, stole the #170,000 vehicle before
OL,14,Fgoing on to fill it up with fuel and
OL,15,Fstop at a restaurant to get something
OL,16,Fto eat.
OL,18,FThe pair broke into a house in High
OL,19,FView Avenue, Keyworth, before stealing
OL,20,Fthe keys to the Range Rover Evoque
OL,21,FSport that was parked outside.
