OL,6,FPolice were called and detectives
OL,7,Ffound that the car had been spotted at
OL,8,Fa petrol station in Loughborough
OL,9,Fshortly after it was stolen around
OL,10,F5:30am on 17 March.
OL,12,FFootage showed Abbott filling the car
OL,13,Fwith petrol before going into the
OL,14,Fpetrol station and paying in cash.
OL,16,FThen, at around 10am on the same
OL,17,Fmorning, the pair arrived at Heart of
OL,18,FEngland Conference and Events Centre
OL,19,Fnear Coventry, where CCTV captured
OL,20,Fthem stopping for food at its on-site
OL,21,Frestaurant.
