OL,3,CYoung burglars caught after going for
OL,4,Cbreakfast in stolen car
OL,6,FThe CCTV images meant police could
OL,7,Fidentify the two men and they were
OL,8,Flater arrested and taken into custody
OL,9,Ffor questioning.
OL,11,FIn his police interview, Abbott denied
OL,12,Fbeing involved in the burglary and
OL,13,Fclaimed he was picked up by the Range
OL,14,FRover after agreeing to a "paid job"
OL,15,Fin order to clear a drug-debt.
OL,17,FBut his story was discredited when
OL,18,Fdetectives found CCTV that showed two
OL,19,Fpeople walking towards the Keyworth
OL,20,Fhouse shortly before it was burgled.
