OL,3,CYoung burglars caught after going for
OL,4,Cbreakfast in stolen car
OL,6,FOne of the individuals could be seen
OL,7,Fwearing clothing that matched what
OL,8,FAbbott had been wearing that same
OL,9,Fmorning. The other person was wearing
OL,10,Fa coat with the same reflective
OL,11,Fpatches on the back, as worn by
OL,12,FStevenson.
OL,14,FSubsequently, both men were charged
OL,15,Fwith burglary and theft.
OL,17,FAbbott, of London Road, Leicester, and
OL,18,FStevenson, of Acacia Crescent,
OL,19,FBedworth, both pleaded guilty.
