OL,6,FThey appeared at Nottingham Crown
OL,7,FCourt and were each sentenced to 18
OL,8,Fmonths in a young offenders
OL,9,Finstitution.
OL,11,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,12,FSergeant James Hirst, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police's county
OL,14,Fburglary team, said: "This matter
OL,15,Funderstandably caused a great deal of
OL,16,Fdistress and anxiety to the victim,
OL,17,Fwho was asleep upstairs when the
OL,18,Fburglary took place.
