OL,6,F"We worked very hard to identify the
OL,7,Foffenders and it is testament to the
OL,8,Fquality of the investigation and the
OL,9,Fcompelling evidence that was secured
OL,10,Fthat both Abbott and Stevenson entered
OL,11,Fguilty pleas.
OL,13,F"These men may have proven themselves
OL,14,Fto be pretty woeful criminals and I am
OL,15,Fpleased we have been able to bring
OL,16,Fthem to justice."
